  <summary date="2017-07-27T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Opioid and Heroin Abuse Crisis Investment Act of 2017

This bill amends the 21st Century Cures Act to make appropriations for FY2019-FY2023 for state grants to address the opioid abuse crisis. States receiving a grant must report on substance abuse services provided to underserved populations, including Native Americans.</summary>
